    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0791b27"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>京兆恒濟寺<persName key="A008984">道成</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0791b28"/><persName key="A008984">釋道成</persName>者，不知何許人也。居<app type="multiplier" xml:id="begd1e22676"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e22676"/><placeName key="PL000000042189">天邑</placeName>，演<lb
ed="T" n="0791b29"/>彼律乘。戒月揚光，圓而不缺；德瓶告實，滿<pb ed="T" n="0791c" xml:id="T50.2061.0791c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0791c01"/>而不傾。當<date from-iso="0656" key="j19606991962581" to-iso="0661">顯慶</date>中，敷《四分》一宗，有同霧<lb
ed="T" n="0791c02"/>市。時<persName key="A002468">文綱律匠</persName>雖先依<persName key="A001519">澄照大師</persName>，後習律<lb
ed="T" n="0791c03"/>文，乃登<persName key="A008984">成</persName>之堂奧矣。又<persName key="A001899">懷素</persName>著述，皆出其<lb
ed="T" n="0791c04"/>門。<date from-iso="0685" key="j19712941972741" to-iso="0689">垂拱</date>中，<persName key="A000332">日照三藏</persName>譯《顯識》等經，<persName key="A002099">天后</persName>詔名<lb
ed="T" n="0791c05"/>德十員助其法化，<persName key="A008984">成</persName>與<persName key="A000661">明恂</persName>、<persName key="A008981">嘉尚</persName>同預證<lb
ed="T" n="0791c06"/>義。由是聲飛神甸，位首方壇，謂之梧桐多<lb
ed="T" n="0791c07"/>棲鳳鳥，謂之芳沚頗秀蘭叢。門生孔多，無<lb
ed="T" n="0791c08"/>過此集，然不詳終所。</p>
    <p xml:id="pT50p0791c0901"><lb
ed="T" n="0791c09"/>系曰：<persName key="A008984">成公</persName>與隋蔣州<persName key="A006381">道成</persName>同號而異實，二<lb
ed="T" n="0791c10"/>者奚先？通曰：「隋<persName key="A006381">成</persName>也精乎《十誦》，著述尤多；<lb
ed="T" n="0791c11"/>唐<persName key="A008984">成</persName>也傳乎《四分》，譯講偕妙。然其撰集則開<lb
ed="T" n="0791c12"/>悟迷淪，究其翻傳則陶甄教道。譬猶後焰<lb
ed="T" n="0791c13"/>靡及乎前光，似寶或慚乎真寶，互有長短，<lb
ed="T" n="0791c14"/>用則無遺也。」</p>
